OL,3,CBonnie Tyler recovering after being in
OL,4,Chospital for emergency surgery
OL,6,FSinger Bonnie Tyler is recovering
OL,7,Fafter being taken to hospital for
OL,8,Femergency surgery.
OL,10,FThe 74-year-old, who was born in
OL,11,FSkewen, is being treated in Faro,
OL,12,FPortugal, where she has a home.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "We are very
OL,15,Fsorry to announce that Bonnie has been
OL,16,Fadmitted to hospital in Faro,
OL,17,FPortugal, where she has a home, for
OL,18,Femergency intestinal surgery.
