OL,3,CBonnie Tyler recovering after being in
OL,4,Chospital for emergency surgery
OL,6,F"The surgery went well and she is now
OL,7,Frecuperating. We know that all of her
OL,8,Ffamily, friends, and fans will be
OL,9,Fconcerned about this news and will be
OL,10,Fwishing her well for a full and swift
OL,11,Frecovery."
